data.message: Created Complete Abstract-to-Digital Translation Framework: Synthesized 10 core principles from Kandinsky, Mondrian, and Malevich into actionable digital design methodology. Validated through 10 principle studies, 1 synthesis masterwork, and 5 production designs. Framework now permanently stored in Duro memory for all future design work.
